metadata.name: The droid Astronaut
metadata.description:
The droid from “real” astronauts.
First character entering The Metaverse, it is curios and suspicious. There is only a thin layer of portal separating reality from virtuality.

Entering The Metaverse NFT collection.
The Idea behind each piece consists of an astronaut suit that represents the newcomers into metaverse. The head and the environment are changing sections, that define different characters.

Artwork info:
Res - 1280x1920
FPS - 30
Animated loop
